WEBVTT

00:03.140 --> 00:04.891
Your orders were not to engage.

00:04.892 --> 00:07.792
Your insubordination
could have cost us dearly.

00:07.811 --> 00:09.461
Troops are accounted for.

00:09.479 --> 00:11.463
Your Excellency, we should attack now.

00:11.481 --> 00:13.465
We take that bridge,

00:13.483 --> 00:15.818
you won't have to worry about
Santa Anna's reinforcements.

