00:25.746 --> 00:27.413
Today, we are one.

00:27.414 --> 00:29.481
We give Texas our allegiance.

00:29.499 --> 00:31.050
We give Texas our lives.

00:31.051 --> 00:32.051
Fire cannon.

00:35.505 --> 00:36.839
Surrender, Mexican,

00:36.840 --> 00:38.507
or I'll kill you deader
than last Tuesday.

00:38.508 --> 00:39.491
Hands up.

00:41.511 --> 00:43.679
We captured Santa Anna!

00:43.680 --> 00:47.400
El Presidente, General, I cannot express

00:47.401 --> 00:49.000
how glad I am to meet you.

00:49.019 --> 00:51.002
Death by firing squad!

01:11.995 --> 01:17.125
