01:17:08.822 --> 01:17:10.657
♪ Sing of Rosa Lee ♪

01:17:10.658 --> 01:17:12.692
♪ But the yellow rose of Texas ♪

01:17:12.693 --> 01:17:15.245
♪ Is the only girl for me ♪

01:17:15.246 --> 01:17:16.913
Yahoo!

01:17:18.832 --> 01:17:21.701
