01:17:24.038 --> 01:17:26.138
♪ She walks along the river ♪

01:17:26.173 --> 01:17:28.591
♪ In the quiet summer night ♪

01:17:28.592 --> 01:17:30.627
♪ She thinks if I remember ♪

01:17:30.628 --> 01:17:33.012
